##Shanghai experience tells you how to prevent epidemic

The papernews

The function introduction, has the connotation the current politics new media

Zou Juan is a reporter for the paper

"finally, the ban CAN BE LIFTED! " Shen Weiming, who works in the Shanghai Free Trade Zone, wrote in a circle of friends on Feb. 16, accompanied by a row of smiling faces.

Shen Weiming is the company's project director, since February 3 from home to Shanghai, Shen Weiming has arranged in the company's talent apartment self-isolation for 14 days, February 17, he can finally "UNBAN" , back to the company to work.

And February 17, it is the day that a lot of Shanghai enterprises resume work. The previous week, many companies in Shanghai were fumbling for the best combination of epidemic prevention and development, and gradually formed a set of effective "Shanghai samples, " according to an interview with the www.thepaper.cn  

This sample, in the enterprise, is responsible for who is responsible for the workers. In the park, is "shop waiter" turned into "floor waiter" ; in the government, is "one enterprise, one policy" to help enterprises.

Development is the hard truth, prevention and control is the hard task, constantly looking for the best combination of epidemic prevention and development. This is the attitude of Shanghai.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Robots disinfect a factory after it resumes work in Zhangjiang, Shanghai. All images in this article are provided for the interviewees

Enterprise: Who is responsible for the employment

If you do not wear a mask in the workshop production, the consequences are very serious.

China Mobile (Shanghai) Industrial Research Institute (hereinafter referred to as "Shangyan") , located in Jinqiao Development Zone, Pudong, has developed a factory mask identification and testing system. Through AI visual detection function, we can infer whether the factory workers wear the mask correctly, and display the mask wearing detection results in real time, warning violations in time.

In addition, for personnel management programs, the institute operates away from closed areas to avoid infection; if suspected cases are detected, the company can quickly screen the contacts with the help of real-time and accurate location tracking capabilities, quickly and accurately identify close contacts, to avoid the company was indiscriminate isolation, reduce costs and losses.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
A tea room is disinfected after an enterprise in Zhangjiang, Shanghai Resumes Work.

Of course, for the enterprise, the norms of management at the same time, the concern for the staff overflow in the details.

At the Tiandi software park in the town of Long March in Putuo District, every company has prepared a set of specific methods to prevent and control the epidemic situation, build up the network of epidemic prevention and control.

Employees of Shanghai Wosai Internet Technology Co. , Ltd. received a "little gift bag" -- a mask, a red envelope, alcohol disinfection, and a safety notice. The Enterprise fully raises the epidemic prevention and control material, reserves the medical mask as the backup, prepares the disinfection spray for each staff, in order to carry on the disinfection to the office supplies, the personal supplies, the company also prepared the warm baby to keep warm for the staff.

Every day, Shanghai Qingke Information Technology Co. , Ltd. . Staff are in the nail "punch card" , fill in "all daily health" information. "Pay attention to keep warm, do not use air conditioning, indoor must wear masks... " Shanghai Longtian Digital Technology Co. , Ltd. for the resumption of employees to send epidemic prevention tips, online and offline ways to strengthen publicity.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
In Fengxian District, the "second floor" is involved in the prevention and control of the epidemic.

Local regulation: "Shop Boy" turns into "floor boy"

In the workshop has the AI to inspect the assistant, in the building then has concurrently the multi-duty "the building primary two" .

99% of the enterprises in the district are small and medium-sized enterprises. Some enterprises and institutions are concentrated in the commercial buildings. On February 6, the district of Fengxian District launched a "second floor" system for 61 office buildings, by the town, the Development Zone (Group Company) and its subordinate park team, designated as the "building two" , as the responsible person, the corresponding guidance to urge the building operators to do a good job of prevention and control.

To urge the building operators to carry out daily cleaning and disinfection, personnel temperature testing, enterprise notification and other work, and make good records and feedback of problems that can not be solved in the building epidemic prevention and control work, fill in the collection of building account registration and every day before 15:00 summary... This is the "second floor" People's Daily.

Liu Wei, chief of the service sector development section at Fengxian District Economic and Social Commission for Economic Development, said that the "shop assistant" , which originally focused on providing good business environment services for enterprises, was now upgraded to "Floor Assistant" , which not only contained the epidemic but also served enterprises well, let the enterprise be able to pass this difficult period safely.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Fengxian District, Hyk Industrial Co. , Ltd. resumed work.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Automated Thermal imaging of workers at work, soles sterilized in Fengxian District.

And the software park in the Long March town of Putuo District has always been recognized and favored by enterprises for its thoughtful "building-length system" service. During the resumption of work by enterprises, the "building-length system" still plays a powerful role, park, "Shop 2" people to the building as a unit, to the floor as the primary responsible person, a business communication, detailed re-construction during the epidemic prevention and control measures.

"which company are you from? Have you returned to Shanghai from other places? Please take your temperature and register your information. " "shop waiter" have on duty, strengthen verification, carefully check the list of returning workers, strictly do a good job of temperature measurement, information registration, pass issued and so on.

The Lujiazui Monetary Authority (HKMA) has set up a "colour management" mechanism for the prevention and control of building outbreaks. The 285 commercial buildings in Lujiazui will be built in accordance with the nature of the commercial buildings, the number of resident enterprises, the number of enterprises returning to work, the on-site environment, the conditions of prevention and control facilities, etc. , to establish four levels of colour control scheme for priority buildings, concern buildings, special buildings and general concern buildings. All building teams and contractors will strictly implement the building management system to ensure that all building works are carried out.

Yangtze River Delta: custom-made "pass" for inter-provincial commuting

Yangtze River Delta Transition Area, many employees cross-province commuting, whether the need to be repeatedly isolated? Do I have to fill in my personal information again and again every day when I go to work?

For example, statistics show that about 3,100 people commute daily from Shanghai Jinshan to Jiashan in Pinghu, Zhejiang Province, and about 1,500 from Jiashan in Pinghu to Jinshan District.

On February 15, on the basis of mutual visits, the three places of Jiashan, Pinghu, and Jinshan jointly launched the "two books and one card" mechanism for mutual recognition of personnel and vehicles, and individuals truthfully filled out the "personal commitment letter" and the "health status information registration form" , that means freedom of movement.

![img](data:image/jpeg;base64,)
Temporary Pass. For Jinshan district

Coincidentally, February 14, in order to solve similar problems, give full play to the advantages of Yangtze River Delta Economic Zone Joint Defense and control, the Shanghai City of Jiading District and Jiangsu Province Kunshan signed the "Jia-kun Memorandum of Joint Defense and Control" .

From that day, a special passageway was opened at the anting checkpoint on the caoan highway. Every day, the workers holding the work-commuting pass could travel between Anting and Huaqiao through the special passageway from 7 to 9 and from 4 to 6. After completing the necessary inspection procedures such as body temperature measurement and vehicle inspection, show me my valid certificate and the temporary pass of anting Huaqiao residential area, and the "person and card" will be allowed to pass in accordance with each other when entering Shanghai, no need to repeat personal information. Personnel Entering Huaqiao territory, will also be in accordance with the local disease control and epidemic prevention requirements for inspection.

Positioning of Shanghai: two-pronged approach to epidemic prevention and development

From the very beginning, Shanghai has had a clear position in terms of both epidemic prevention and development.

On Feb. 8, the Leading Group for the prevention and control of pneumonia in Shanghai's COVID-19 held a meeting on the eve of resuming work. Secretary of the CPC Shanghai Committee, Municipal Epidemic Prevention and Control Work Leading Group leader Li Qiang chaired the meeting and spoke.

The meeting stressed that enterprises to do a good job in order to resume work, the strict implementation of various units to prevent and control the main responsibility of the epidemic. Explore flexible working hours, staggered work, rotation to work, remote work, work at home, flexible attendance management and other effective ways. To fully support the development of enterprises, comprehensive measures, accurate measures to deal with uncertainty with policy certainty, to help enterprises stable confidence, stable expectations.

This has become a "guide" for Shanghai's epidemic prevention and development work.

February 10, the first day of an orderly resumption of work in Shanghai enterprises. In the afternoon, Li Qiang went to the traffic hub, commercial buildings to check the implementation of the prevention and control work of the new pneumonia. That night, the Standing Committee of the Shanghai Municipal Party Committee held a meeting, clearly required that the territorial control package system to be detailed.

On the morning of February 13, Li Qiang came to Pudong to inspect the CDC, resume work enterprises, and into the subway Kanahashi Station, Xujiahui Station, on-site inspection of the epidemic prevention and control work implementation. In the afternoon, the Standing Committee of the Shanghai Municipal Committee held a meeting, calling for the overall management of the current epidemic prevention and control and Work Safety.

Top-down attention, in return for the efficient implementation of policies.

On Feb. 8, Shanghai issued 28 comprehensive policy measures to fully support enterprises in fighting the epidemic, including tax incentives, rent relief, financial support and so on. Shanghai's 16 districts have rolled out detailed support plans. "One enterprise, one policy" , "one matter, one discussion" has become the "standard" of the government's precise policy.

On February 10,228 enterprises with financing difficulties in Pudong district opened a green passage for bypass banks. MELALEUCA, the largest tax payer in Fengxian District, needs only 2,000 masks to start construction. The relevant authorities in the region immediately helped solve the problem and let enterprises feel the government's help.

"there is not a winter that will not pass, and not a spring that will not come. It's spring in Shanghai, the epidemic will pass, and the best way to get out of the shadow of the epidemic and resume production is for enterprises, territories and governments to work together." Said a street merchant.
